Title: Gum Power Rangers Timer Light Toothbrush - Soft (3 Pack)
Description: Plaque and cavities don’t stand a chance with the Power Rangers! The GUM® Power Rangers™ Timer Light toothbrush is an illuminated and colorful way to educate your child about the importance of brushing, the prevention of plaque buildup, and the foundations for a lifelong healthy mouth. Many professional organizations worldwide, including the American Dental Association, endorse a two-minute minimum brushing time for effective cleaning and plaque removal, however, the majority of children (and adults) brush for less than one minute. The GUM® Power Rangers™ Timer Light toothbrush has LED lights that illuminate the entire brush and flash for 60 seconds indicating the minimum time to be spent on each row of teeth (one minute on the top and one minute on the bottom). The GUM® Power Rangers™ Timer Light toothbrush features the Dome Trim® bristle design. The raised center bristles have been trimmed to form a dome shape that provides greater contact with the tooth surface and reaches under the gum line. The outer row of bristles is slightly more flexible than the center rows so that the soft, more flexible bristles will gently clean under the gumline while the center, slightly stiffer rows will clean the tooth surfaces. The suction cup base holds the toothbrush upright, when not in use, which helps keep bristles clean and reduces clutter. The GUM® Power Rangers™ Timer Light toothbrush is entertaining for children and comes in three different colors/characters: Red- = Red Ranger, Blue = Blue Ranger and Yellow = Black Ranger. Collect them all! A fun and motivating toothbrush for children over three years old! Brush for at least two minutes twice a day, morning and night to stay on the right course for a lifelong healthy smile. Replace toothbrush every three months or, sooner, if brush head appears worn. This product is not a toy and should always be used with adult supervision. Not intended for children under three years of age.
